    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "O that men would praise the Lord for his goodness,.... Or, \"confess to the Lord his goodness or grace\", or \"mercy\" (g); own and acknowledge it, in delivering them from such a state of darkness and death, of thraldom and captivity; see ",
        "children": []
