      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And for his wonderful works to the children of men! or, \"confess\" them before them; relate and declare them to them, what wonderful things he has done for them; that they may be affected with them, and that they may praise his name together; See Gill on Psalm 107:9. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
